{"name":"Voice of the Spirits","type":"item","img":"icons/magic/perception/eye-ringed-glow-angry-small-teal.webp","system":{"itemType":"scenarioGift","description":"With the right peace and focus, you can open your mind to the spirit world and communicate with restless souls. Spend 1 Soma to contact any creature with the Spirit Gift that you've previously encountered. You can communicate with the Spirit telepathically and understand what it says, even across distances. This communion lasts for the duration of a Scene or until you release it.","somaCost":1,"requirement":"You have been in contact with either the Spirit or Spiritualist Gifts (encountered Yvonne, Restless Spirits, or met Alizée).","scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness","notes":"This Gift allows communication with any spirit the Hunter has previously met, including Yvonne, the Restless Spirits in the catacombs, or any other creature with the Spirit Gift. It doesn't control spirits, only enables dialogue. Useful for: 1) Negotiating with Yvonne, 2) Learning information from Restless Spirits about her presence, 3) Understanding spirit motivations. The connection is empathic and telepathic—spirits can't lie through it but can refuse to answer."},"_id":"33b2f3f74a135553"}
{"name":"Exorcist","type":"item","img":"icons/magic/holy/prayer-hands-glowing-yellow.webp","system":{"itemType":"scenarioGift","description":"You have learned how to use your skills against restless Spirits through sacred rites, prayers, blessed objects, or mystical practices. All your actions can now affect targets who have the Spirit Gift, bypassing their immunity to physical harm. Additionally, all Wounds you inflict on Spirits cannot be ignored or regenerated by the Spirit Gift—your attacks harm their spiritual essence permanently.","somaCost":0,"requirement":"Have a Church or Magic-related Descriptor AND talk to Father Adrien or Alizée about practices used against Spirits.","scenario":"The Smile in the Darkness","notes":"This Gift makes the Hunter a true spirit hunter, capable of permanently harming entities like Yvonne and the Restless Spirits. Requirement details: 1) Must have appropriate Descriptor (priest, mage, witch hunter, occultist, etc.), 2) Must learn exorcism techniques from either Adrien (prayers, holy water, blessed weapons) or Alizée (spiritualist methods, binding rituals). Mechanical impact: Completely bypasses Spirit Gift's immunity and regeneration. The Hunter's sword, bullets, or bare hands can now wound spirit essence directly. Wounds dealt are permanent and don't heal when spirits dissipate. This is crucial for defeating Yvonne permanently—without this or magic, she regenerates endlessly."},"_id":"5d900e736e714329"}
